org.apache.hawq.pxf.plugins.hdfs

Class HdfsSplittableDataAccessor

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.hawq.pxf.api.utilities.Plugin
      • org.apache.hawq.pxf.plugins.hdfs.HdfsSplittableDataAccessor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ReadAccessor
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AvroFileAccessor, HiveAccessor, LineBreakAccessor, SequenceFileAccessor

    public abstract class HdfsSplittableDataAccessor
extends Plugin
implements ReadAccessor
    Accessor for accessing a splittable HDFS data sources. HDFS will divide the file into splits based on an internal decision (by default, the block size is also the split size). Accessors that require such base functionality should extend this class.
